<lb n="1097b03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="1" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="1097002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】近江園城寺藏古寫本</note><note place="inline">外題</note>日本比丘圓珍入唐求法目
